{"thig13.2:0.1":"Therigatha 13.2 ","thig13.2:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thig13.2:0.3":"Rohinitherigatha ","thig13.2:1.1":"“‘Samana’ti bhoti supi, ","thig13.2:1.2":"‘samana’ti pabujjhasi; ","thig13.2:1.3":"Samananeva kittesi, ","thig13.2:1.4":"samani nuna bhavissasi. ","thig13.2:2.1":"Vipulam annanca pananca, ","thig13.2:2.2":"samananam paveccasi; ","thig13.2:2.3":"Rohini dani pucchami, ","thig13.2:2.4":"kena te samana piya. ","thig13.2:3.1":"Akammakama alasa, ","thig13.2:3.2":"paradattupajivino; ","thig13.2:3.3":"Asamsuka sadukama, ","thig13.2:3.4":"kena te samana piya”. ","thig13.2:4.1":"“Cirassam vata mam tata, ","thig13.2:4.2":"samananam paripucchasi; ","thig13.2:4.3":"Tesam te kittayissami, ","thig13.2:4.4":"pannasilaparakkamam. ","thig13.2:5.1":"Kammakama analasa, ","thig13.2:5.2":"kammasetthassa karaka; ","thig13.2:5.3":"Ragam dosam pajahanti, ","thig13.2:5.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:6.1":"Tini papassa mulani, ","thig13.2:6.2":"dhunanti sucikarino; ","thig13.2:6.3":"Sabbam papam pahinesam, ","thig13.2:6.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:7.1":"Kayakammam suci nesam, ","thig13.2:7.2":"vacikammanca tadisam; ","thig13.2:7.3":"Manokammam suci nesam, ","thig13.2:7.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:8.1":"Vimala sankhamuttava, ","thig13.2:8.2":"suddha santarabahira; ","thig13.2:8.3":"Punna sukkana dhammanam, ","thig13.2:8.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:9.1":"Bahussuta dhammadhara, ","thig13.2:9.2":"ariya dhammajivino; ","thig13.2:9.3":"Attham dhammanca desenti, ","thig13.2:9.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:10.1":"Bahussuta dhammadhara, ","thig13.2:10.2":"ariya dhammajivino; ","thig13.2:10.3":"Ekaggacitta satimanto, ","thig13.2:10.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:11.1":"Durangama satimanto, ","thig13.2:11.2":"mantabhani anuddhata; ","thig13.2:11.3":"Dukkhassantam pajananti, ","thig13.2:11.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:12.1":"Yasma gama pakkamanti, ","thig13.2:12.2":"na vilokenti kincanam; ","thig13.2:12.3":"Anapekkhava gacchanti, ","thig13.2:12.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:13.1":"Na te sam kotthe openti, ","thig13.2:13.2":"na kumbhim na khalopiyam; ","thig13.2:13.3":"Parinitthitamesana, ","thig13.2:13.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:14.1":"Na te hirannam ganhanti, ","thig13.2:14.2":"na suvannam na rupiyam; ","thig13.2:14.3":"Paccuppannena yapenti, ","thig13.2:14.4":"tena me samana piya. ","thig13.2:15.1":"Nanakula pabbajita, ","thig13.2:15.2":"nanajanapadehi ca; ","thig13.2:15.3":"Annamannam piyayanti, ","thig13.2:15.4":"tena me samana piya”. ","thig13.2:16.1":"“Atthaya vata no bhoti, ","thig13.2:16.2":"kule jatasi rohini; ","thig13.2:16.3":"Saddha buddhe ca dhamme ca, ","thig13.2:16.4":"sanghe ca tibbagarava. ","thig13.2:17.1":"Tuvam hetam pajanasi, ","thig13.2:17.2":"punnakkhettam anuttaram; ","thig13.2:17.3":"Amhampi ete samana, ","thig13.2:17.4":"patiganhanti dakkhinam. ","thig13.2:18.1":"Patitthito hettha yanno, ","thig13.2:18.2":"vipulo no bhavissati”; ","thig13.2:18.3":"“Sace bhayasi dukkhassa, ","thig13.2:18.4":"sace te dukkhamappiyam. ","thig13.2:19.1":"Upehi saranam buddham, ","thig13.2:19.2":"dhammam sanghanca tadinam; ","thig13.2:19.3":"Samadiyahi silani, ","thig13.2:19.4":"tam te atthaya hehiti”. ","thig13.2:20.1":"“Upemi saranam buddham, ","thig13.2:20.2":"dhammam sanghanca tadinam; ","thig13.2:20.3":"Samadiyami silani, ","thig13.2:20.4":"tam me atthaya hehiti. ","thig13.2:21.1":"Brahmabandhu pure asim, ","thig13.2:21.2":"so idanimhi brahmano; ","thig13.2:21.3":"Tevijjo sottiyo camhi, ","thig13.2:21.4":"vedagu camhi nhatako”. ","thig13.2:22.1":"… Rohini theri …. "}